  "texts": [
    "Freezing \"Do not run!\"",
    "is first universal advice to everyone who suddenly finds themselves in dangerous proximity to a predator.",
    "Popular belief that it would take a lot of courage not to run away when seeing a deadly predator at close quarters is not correct.",
    "As a matter of fact, people in life-threatening situations usually freeze and cannot move, even if they want to.",
    "Although some still may try to run away in a state of panic, the more natural (and often life-saving) response, also instinctive, is to freeze."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}